the internet in ways

00:16:59.700 --> 00:17:01.700
we have never seen before.

00:17:01.700 --> 00:17:03.860
They live on their phones.

00:17:03.860 --> 00:17:07.720
They use it to communicate,
learn new things,

00:17:07.720 --> 00:17:11.650
gain knowledge,
entertain themselves.

00:17:11.650 --> 00:17:15.310
They tap an icon,
expect a car to show up.

00:17:15.310 --> 00:17:17.069
They talk to their
phones and even

00:17:17.069 --> 00:17:18.550
expect music to
play in the living

00:17:18.550 --> 00:17:22.730
room or, sometimes, groceries
to show up at the front door.

00:17:22.730 --> 00:17:25.210
So we are pushing
ourselves really hard,

00:17:25.210 --> 00:17:27.310
so that Google is
evolving and staying

00:17:27.310 --> 00:17:30.130
a step ahead of our users.

