bit about the future.

00:25:09.190 --> 00:25:12.320
We want to show you the kind
of things we ask [INAUDIBLE]

00:25:12.320 --> 00:25:13.895
to be able to do.

00:25:13.895 --> 00:25:16.400
Now, let me do that
with an example.

00:25:16.400 --> 00:25:17.720
Here's a common situation.

00:25:17.720 --> 00:25:18.970
It's Friday night.

00:25:18.970 --> 00:25:21.770
I'm sure many of you can
relate to it back home.

00:25:21.770 --> 00:25:23.735
And I want to take
my family to a movie.

00:25:23.735 --> 00:25:25.970
You know, you normally
pull out your phone,

00:25:25.970 --> 00:25:28.680
research movies,
look at the reviews,

00:25:28.680 --> 00:25:32.190
find shows nearby, and
try to book a ticket.

00:25:32.190 --> 00:25:35.320
We want to be there in
