if you ask that question,

00:25:42.500 --> 00:25:46.420
we do return movie results, but
we want to go a step further.

00:25:46.420 --> 00:25:49.620
We want to send your
context and maybe suggest

00:25:49.620 --> 00:25:53.440
three relevant movies which
you would like nearby.

00:25:53.440 --> 00:25:56.840
I should be able to look at
it and maybe tell Google,

00:25:56.840 --> 00:25:59.160
