options and maybe even ask me,

00:26:07.480 --> 00:26:10.610
would you like four
tickets to any of these?

00:26:10.610 --> 00:26:13.930
And if I say, sure,
let's do "Jungle Book,"

00:26:13.930 --> 00:26:16.170
it should go ahead
and get the tickets

00:26:16.170 --> 00:26:19.673
and have them ready waiting
for me when I need it.

00:26:19.673 --> 00:26:24.110
[APPLAUSE]

00:26:25.590 --> 00:26:29.600
As you can see, I engage in
a conversation with Google,

00:26:29.600 --> 00:26:33.760
and it helped me get
things done in my context.

00:26:33.760 --> 00:26:38.010
And by the way, this is just
one version of the conversation.

00:26:38.010 --> 00:26:40.960
This could have gone
many, many different ways.

00:26:40.960 --> 00:26:44.050
For example, when Google
returned the results,

00:26:44.050 --> 00:26:47.880
I could've asked, is
"Jungle Book" any good?

00:26:47.880 --> 00:26:50.930
And Google could have
given me the reviews

00:26:50.930 --> 00:26:52.897
and maybe even
shown me a trailer.

00:26:52.897 --> 00:26:54.230
And by the way, I saw the movie.

00:26:54.230 --> 00:26:58.150
It's terrific and hope
you get to see it as well.

00:26:58.150 --> 00:27:01.260
Every single conversation
is different.

00:27:01.260 --> 00:27:03.980
Every single context
is different.

00:27:03.980 --> 00:27:07.380
And we are working hard
to do this for billions

00:27:07.380 --> 00:27:10.520
of conversations for
billions of users

00:27:10.520 --> 00:27:13.730
around the world for everyone.

00:27:13.730 --> 00:27:16.640
We think of the
Assistant as an ambient

00:27:16.640 --> 00:27:20.570
experience that
extends across devices.

00:27:20.570 --> 00:27:24.300
I think computing is poised
to evolve beyond just phones.

00:27:24.300 --> 00:27:27.870
It'll be in the context
of a user's daily life.

00:27:27.870 --> 00:27:31.370
It'll be on their phones,
devices they wear,

00:27:31.370 --> 00:27:35.160
in their cars, and even
in their living rooms.

00:27:35.160 --> 00:27:39.530
For example, if you're in one of
the 100 different Android Auto

00:27:39.530 --> 00:27:42.200
models and you're
driving and you say,

00:27:42.200 --> 00:27:44.590
let's have curry
tonight, we know

00:27:44.590 --> 00:27:47.880
the Warriors are on tonight
and Steph Curry is playing,

00:27:47.880 --> 00:27:50.170
but do you know all you're
looking for is food.

00:27:50.170 --> 00:27:53.190
And we should be
smart, order that food,

00:27:53.190 --> 00:27:55.790
and let you know
when it is ready

00:27:55.790 --> 00:28:00.670
and maybe even have it
waiting for you at your home.

