newborn baby can all

00:59:37.040 --> 00:59:39.530
draw you into the
moment, making calls

00:59:39.530 --> 00:59:41.990
feel spontaneous and natural.

00:59:41.990 --> 00:59:45.140
And once you pick up, Duo
puts you right into the call,

00:59:45.140 --> 00:59:47.760
seamlessly transitioning
from the live preview

00:59:47.760 --> 00:59:49.710
to the live call.

00:59:49.710 --> 00:59:51.430
Knock Knock totally
changes what it's

00:59:51.430 --> 00:59:53.910
like to receive a video call.

