network quality multiple times

01:02:14.860 --> 01:02:17.430
per second, allowing
to degrade gracefully

01:02:17.430 --> 01:02:20.340
when bandwidth is limited
and to seamlessly switch

01:02:20.340 --> 01:02:22.470
between Wi-Fi and cellular.

01:02:22.470 --> 01:02:24.410
