happens automatically

01:02:24.410 --> 01:02:28.310
behind the scenes, so you
don't have to worry about it.

01:02:28.310 --> 01:02:31.900
All this technology combines
with a smooth interface

01:02:31.900 --> 01:02:34.560
that fades away,
allowing you to focus

01:02:34.560 --> 01:02:38.700
on each other in beautiful
HD video and audio.

01:02:38.700 --> 01:02:40.560
This is what makes
Duo a video calling

01:02:40.560 --> 01:02:44.370
experience that feels unlike
anything you've used before.

