extended the OpenGL standard

01:08:16.130 --> 01:08:18.910
to bring advanced graphics
capabilities, usually found

01:08:18.910 --> 01:08:22.020
on the desktop and game
consoles, to mobile.

01:08:22.020 --> 01:08:24.870
