so you can use the same APIs

01:08:43.810 --> 01:08:47.550
and graphics assets and shaders
on the desktop as well as

01:08:47.550 --> 01:08:48.950
mobile.

01:08:48.950 --> 01:08:53.250
Because Vulkan has a lower
CPU overhead than OpenGL,

01:08:53.250 --> 01:08:54.740
game developers
are able to squeeze

01:08:54.740 --> 01:08:58.439
in more effects per frame while
still maintaining a high frame

01:08:58.439 --> 01:08:59.550
rate.

