01:29:07.240 --> 01:29:10.120
So something else that's going
to be awesome in Daydream

01:29:10.120 --> 01:29:11.240
is games.

01:29:11.240 --> 01:29:14.300
We've been working with the
likes of Ubisoft and CCP,

01:29:14.300 --> 01:29:16.260
NetEase, and Electronic Arts.

01:29:16.260 --> 01:29:18.350
And these amazing
developers are creating

01:29:18.350 --> 01:29:20.970
games that take advantage of
all that we've talked about.

01:29:20.970 --> 01:29:25.090
And there are some really
neat things in the works.

01:29:25.090 --> 01:29:28.800
We've also been working
on some of our own apps.

01:29:28.800 --> 01:29:31.260
Google Play Movies is
coming to Daydream,

01:29:31.260 --> 01:29:35.120
complete with high
definition, DRM video support.

01:29:35.120 --> 01:29:37.440
That means you'll be able
to watch movies and TV

01:29:37.440 --> 01:29:40.760
shows from play, but in
a virtual movie theater.

01:29:40.760 --> 01:29:42.520
Street View is
coming to Daydream,

01:29:42.520 --> 01:29:44.950
